<br>
skewers <br>
block, skewer sketch, water flask, quality firing sheet <br>
trivial at 21 <br>
<br>
ceramic lining <br>
small block, ceramic lining sketch, water flask, quality firing sheet <br>
trivial at 36 <br>
<br>
pot (used in baking)<br>
large block, pot sketch, water flask, metal bits (made by a smith) high quality firing sheet <br>
trivial at 56 <br>
<br>
smoker (used in baking)<br>
large block, smoker sketch, water flask, 2 high quality firing sheets <br>
trivial at 82 <br>
<br>
cookie cutters (fun way of shaping cookies)<br>
small block, appropriate cookie template, water flask, high quality firing sheet <br>
trivial at 102 <br>
<br>
pie tin (baking again)<br>
2 blocks, pie tin sketch, water flask, high quality firing sheet trivial at 115 <br>
<br>
medium bowl <br>
block, medium bowl sketch, water flask, 2 high quality firing sheets <br>
trivial at 122 <br>
<br>
small wisdom deity <br>
large block ,deity sketch, water flask, sands of Ro(seen on sand giants in North and South Ro) ( 2 WIS, CLR, DRU) equips in ranged,  high quality firing sheet <br>
trivial at 135 <br>
<br>
large bowl <br>
large block, large bowl sketch, water flask, glass shards, high quality firing sheet <br>
trivial at 148 <br>
<br>
lined poison vial <br>
small block, lined vial sketch, water flask, &lt;old world pelt or skin other than ruined, including zombie skins**&gt;  high quality firing sheet <br>
trivial at 168 <br>
<br>
sealed poison vial <br>
